---
title: Red Pesto Chicken Melts with Potato Wedges & Garden Salad
description: Our red pesto is a pocket rocket, jam-packed with flavour thanks to sun-dried tomatoes, basil and chargrilled capsicum. Spread it over chicken breast and sprinkle with cheese to make these irresistible chicken melts, and add some potato wedges and salad to create a meal that's got 'delicious' written all over it!
